<CommercialHero
  title="French Top Range Repair Los Angeles"
  subtitle="Solid steel plate cooking surface. Vulcan VR-FT, Wolf Challenger XL FT, Garland Master FT, Montague Legend FT across LA, OC, Ventura. Specialty trade. $120 commercial diagnostic. BHGS #A49573."
  heroImageTitle="French Top Range Repair"
